trans-unit.source: Represents the configuration section for authentication modules.
trans-unit.target: 表示驗證模組的組態區段。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModulesSection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModulesSection"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: This constructor adds the <xref:System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElementCollection> class to the <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement.Properties%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 這個建構函式加入<xref:System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElementCollection>類別<xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement.Properties%2A>屬性。</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement.Properties%2A> </xref:System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElementCollection>

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of authentication modules in the section.
trans-unit.target: 取得區段中的驗證模組的集合。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElementCollection> returned by this property contains one <xref:System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElement> for each authentication module in the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElementCollection>傳回此屬性包含一個<xref:System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElement>組態檔中的每個驗證模組。</xref:System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElement> </xref:System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElementCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElementCollection"></xref> that contains the registered authentication modules.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElementCollection"> </xref> ，其中包含已註冊的驗證模組。
